methods.computeRedirections:
Stamps the left-hand-side values with the corresponding right hand side.

 The rightKeyIndices are parallel to the stamp values in rightStamps; and used to compute a new chunk of redirections
 parallel to leftStamps.

:param leftStamps: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Chunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Values>
:param rightStamps: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Chunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Values>
:param rightKeyIndices: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.LongChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.KeyIndices>
:param leftRedirections: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.WritableLongChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.KeyIndices>
